* Taylor, John W.R. &quot;Douglas DB-7, A-20 Havoc, and Boston (Bombers) and Douglas DB-7, Havoc, P-70 (Fighters).&quot; &quot;Combat Aircraft of the World from 1909 to the present&quot;. New York: G.P. Putnam&#x27;s Sons, 1969. .
