* “Fritz Eichenberg (1901-1990)” Brier Hill Gallery.
* “Fritz Eichenberg: 1901–1990” Terra Foundation for American Art.
* Oral history interview with Fritz Eichenberg (3 December 1964) at the Archives of American Art, Smithsonian Institution (aaa.si.edu)
* Fritz Eichenberg at Library of Congress, with 520 library catalog records.
